In today's shocking news, we cover the story of Woo May Hoe, a Singaporean woman who claimed to be a deity for eight years, attracting followers with promises of redemption and healing. Instead, she manipulated them, causing severe physical pain and financial loss. Woo was finally sentenced to 10.5 years in prison in June 2024. Watch the full story and share your thoughts in the comments. Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe to Twenty Two Thirty for more intriguing stories.

Namun, dia memanipulasi mereka, menyebabkan rasa sakit fisik yang parah dan kerugian finansial. Woo akhirnya dijatuhi hukuman 10,5 tahun penjara pada Juni 2024.
